Here you see the young author
of Williwaw at the age of 19,


7
00:01:41.481 --> 00:01:43.190
still in uniform.

8
00:01:44.610 --> 00:01:47.069
Here, above the bathtub,
in the place of honor,


9
00:01:47.279 --> 00:01:50.573
are the debates
