Cameras, please. Cameras.

13
00:02:25.442 --> 00:02:26.859
William F. Buckley.

14
00:02:31.114 --> 00:02:32.990
Thank you very much,
ladies and gentlemen.


15
00:02:34.618 --> 00:02:36.285
