32
00:03:52.279 --> 00:03:55.531
speed and efficiency in
the nerve centers of NBC News.


33
00:03:55.866 --> 00:03:59.493
News was this big, bland center

34
00:03:59.661 --> 00:04:02.955
that determined for us
what America was.


35
00:04:03.123 --> 00:04:06.167
Which was white, Anglo
-Saxon,

36
00:04:06.334 --> 00:04:08.586
there were never any vowels
