37
00:04:08.837 --> 00:04:10.296
Chet Huntley and
David Brinkley


38
00:04:10.589 --> 00:04:12.006
still are the team supreme

39
00:04:12.174 --> 00:04:13.924
in the art of easygoing commentary.

40
00:04:15.385 --> 00:04:19.013
Networks, did they deal
in controversy? No!


41
00:04:19.473 --> 00:04:21.891
Did they invite controversy? No!

